Hi,

remember one of the rules of Unit test, test in isolation, what this means
is that no tests should depend on something else that is doen in another, I
would recommend that you rework the tests so they run so. I would also
recommend that you create a Fixture that does all the setup for the 3 tests,
the tests can then setup and teardown as needed for the tests to suceed.



